{"ENIGMA":[{"def":"Relating to or resembling an enigma; not easily explained or accounted for; darkly expressed; obscure; puzzling; as, an enigmatical answer.","pos":""}],"ENIGMATICALLY":[{"def":"Darkly; obscurely.","pos":""}],"ENIGMATIST":[{"def":"One who makes, or talks in, enigmas.","pos":""}],"ENIGMATIZE":[{"def":"To make, or talk in, enigmas; to deal in riddles.","pos":""},{"def":"The art of making or of solving enigmas.","pos":""}],"ENISLED":[{"def":"Placed alone or apart, as if on an island; severed, as an island.","pos":""}]}